<a name="blade_of_abrogation"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Blade of Abrogation</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">1H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 10.51<BR>
Damage 20 - Delay 39<BR>
Weight: 7.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">SHD</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +7) (INT +3) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in the Plane of Air.<BR>

